=== Recommended approach ===
Don't decode dir names. Instead:
1. List all subdirs in ~/.gsd/sessions/
2. For each subdir + JSONL file, read first line (session record)
3. Extract cwd from session record
4. Match cwd against workspace paths
This avoids the lossy encoding/decoding problem entirely.
